casebody.data:
Chris HANSEN, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 8623. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 11, 1937. M. B. Moore, of Oakland, Cal., and Wm. L. Hacker, of Reno, Nev., for appellant. E. P. Carville, U. S. Atty., of Reno, Nev.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon request of appellant, his counsel ordered appeal herein dismissed, that a judgment of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and the mandate of this court issued forthwith.
